      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK ATOM (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (26.46) in a Restricted WIN H at Warragul. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Rates on top in this line up. GALLOPING JESSIE (4) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at this track over 350m (20.52). Better than last start and can bounce back. PAW YAZ (7) was never in contention last time after being shuffled back early at Warragul, but prior to that won easily by 4 lengths at Warragul (22.98) beating Tootsie in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 on May 14. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. PAW VANNA (5) has definite claims at her first try at this circuit.",
